snippet.title: Amber Heard Looks Sexy At LAX In the Same Outfit She Arrived In LA Wearing Two Days Before
snippet.description: Friday, June 26, 2015 - Amber Heard arrives at LAX airport for an outgoing flight. The 29-year-old actress and wife of Johnny Depp looks casual cool, wearing nearly the same outfit as when she arrived in Los Angeles two days earlier, a white ripped t-shirt, skinny black jeans. While in town for the Magic Mike XXL premiere Thursday night where she oozed sex appeal in a blue slinky dress, Amber comments on Friday's US Supreme Court ruling to legalize same sex marriage in all 50 states instead by saying, "It's a great day for everybody."
